h3. Summary
Confluence will attempt to restart itself during an import if the import is too long causing the site import to fail.

h3. Environment
* Confluence Cloud 1000.1035.0 


h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Perform a site import which will take more than 2 hours to complete. 

h3. Expected Results
Site import is successful

h3. Actual Results
Site import fails saying a restart occurred during the operation.
 
h3. Notes
When looking at Confluence logs, we can see a restart happening during the attachments upload step . During that step, Confluence will spam the following in CLOGS:
