h3.Workaround
Disable monitoring in SOPS room for the duration of the import.
Prevent Confluence from fixing itself by using the following commands every 30 minutes (Confluence check if the file has been updated for the past 2 hours, if not it will try to fix itself):
{code}touch /tmp/conf_autofix_lock{code}

